Package: drake.hasty
Title: Hasty Mode for the Drake R Package
Description: This package is just a sandbox for the drake R package.
  It is unofficial, and it will never go to CRAN or Bioconductor.
  For more information, please visit
  <https://ropenscilabs.github.io/drake-manual/hpc.html#hasty-mode>.
  Hasty mode sacrifices reproducibility to gain speed.
  Use at your own risk.
Version: 0.0.0
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/wlandau/drake.hasty
BugReports: https://github.com/wlandau/drake.hasty/issues
